<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id7a31d0b1-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1982-10-08">Oct. 8, 1982</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/97/290/s312">section 312 of Pub. L. 97–290</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s4011">section 4011 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
